# Netlify redirects configuration

# www to non-www redirect (301 permanent redirect)
https://www.keystoneclub.co.kr/* https://keystoneclub.co.kr/:splat 301!
http://www.keystoneclub.co.kr/* https://keystoneclub.co.kr/:splat 301!

# Force HTTPS redirect
http://keystoneclub.co.kr/* https://keystoneclub.co.kr/:splat 301!

# Block access to sitemap and other crawler files
/sitemap.xml 404
/sitemap.txt 404
/sitemap 404
/robots 404

# Block access to old reserve-detail files for additional security
/reserve-detail-*.html /reserve.html 301

# Add security headers
/*
  X-Frame-Options: DENY
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  X-XSS-Protection: 1; mode=block
  Referrer-Policy: no-referrer
  
# SPA routing fallback (for single page application routing)
/*    /index.html   200